The paper discusses virtualization techniques and their applicability in on-demand computing, which falls under the category of distributed computing (cs.DC). The focus on security also suggests the category of cryptography and security (cs.CR). The paper also discusses the properties of virtual machine systems, which falls under the category of software engineering (cs.SE) and operating systems (cs.OS). Finally, the paper discusses the potential for higher utilization of computing resources, which falls under the category of networking and internet architecture (cs.NI).
